datasem.xtext.kanban.domainmodel.kanbanmodel

Interface Statement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StatementImpl

    public interface Statement
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Statement'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Is Action
    • Action Statement
    • Is Change State
    • Change State Statement
    • Is Declaration
    • Declaration Statement
    • Is If Expression
    • If Expression
    • Is For Expression
    • For Expression
    • Is While Expression
    • While Expression
    • Assert Statement

    See Also:
    KanbanmodelPackage.getStatement()
